    "message": "🗓️ **Monday Kickoff — Set Your Week Up Right**\n\nBefore the week gets away from you, spend 5 minutes locking in your plan:\n\n**1. Top 3 Priorities**\n• What must ship or move forward this week?\n• Rank them — if you only finish one, which one?\n\n**2. Key Meetings / Deadlines**\n• Anything time-sensitive worth noting?\n• Prep needed before a meeting?\n\n**3. Risks or Dependencies**\n• Waiting on anyone? Flag it now, not Friday.\n• Anything that could derail your top priority?\n\n**Save it:** Write a short checklist to `memory/weekly-plan-YYYY-MM-DD.md` (replace YYYY-MM-DD with today's date).\n\nThis becomes your Friday scorecard. Future-you will thank you. ✊"
